description:
As people are becoming sick from eating food sold at the marketplaces, its time to take our health into our own hands. The only way we can be sure of what we are eating is if we actually get to work and grow it ourselves. In this video we will show our viewers how to work with clay soil which is very hard to work with. We added peat moss and soil conditioner into the soil to make it manageable and made mounds as a growing medium.

Contact: gardenevangelist@gmail.com
